          </zone>
          <zone forceUpdate='true' h='3763' id='16' type-v2='text' w='99034' x='483' y='95297'>
            <formatted-text>
              <run bold='true'>Key Insights</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true'>• Organic Search is the primary acquisition channel, contributing the largest share of website traffic.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true'>• Google and YouTube are the top traffic sources, indicating strong search and video platform performance.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true'>• Desktop users account for the majority of traffic, suggesting desktop-first optimization should remain a priority.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true'>• The United States generates the highest number of visits, followed by India and the United Kingdom.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true'>• Paid Search contributes a relatively small share of traffic, indicating an opportunity to review advertising strategies.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true'>Recommendations</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true'>• Increase investment in high-performing organic and social channels.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true'>• Optimize landing pages for mobile users to improve engagement.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true'>• Expand marketing campaigns in high-performing regions such as the United States and India.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true'>• Evaluate paid search campaigns to improve ROI and traffic contribution.</run>
            </formatted-text>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='margin' value='4' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
      </zones>
